  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Welcome to BEAN Coffee Task Manager!\n\nI'm here to help you capture ideas and tasks on the go. Just send me:\n\u2022 Product ideas\n\u2022 Marketing suggestions\n\u2022 Operations to-dos\n\u2022 Any business thoughts\n\nExample: 'Add caramel macchiato to menu' or 'Need to fix espresso machine urgently'\n\nWhat's on your mind?",
